---
title: Herby Beef Meatball Pita Platter with Cucumber Salad, Feta Sauce & Red Pepper Hummus
description: Build the sandwich of your dreams with our vibrant Mediterranean-style pita board that’s piled high with hearty cumin-spiced beef meatballs, tangy feta-yogurt sauce, juicy tomato-cucumber salad, and smoky red pepper hummus. Pile your combination of choice onto toasty-warm pitas, or create a custom plate of tasty tidbits and dip, dunk, and scoop as you please. Just don’t forget to photograph this impressive spread before you dig in!
